DARPA helped create the internet, self-driving cars, and GPS — but now they want to create something far more unsettling: tools to predict and control your behavior. In this episode, I dive into DARPA’s new AI project aimed at forecasting human actions at scale. From pandemic origins to Minority Report-style surveillance, we explore the line between innovation and total control — and ask what it means for your freedom.
